  "prompt": "Which is the best plan for international calling in India for people in UAE?",
  "response": "For people in the UAE making international calls to India, several options are available:\n\n1. Mobile Carrier Plans\n- Etisalat and Du offer international calling packages to India\n- Monthly plans with fixed rates\n- Vary in price and call duration\n\n2. VoIP Services\n- WhatsApp Calling (Free)\n- Skype\n- Google Voice\n- Viber\n- Offers low-cost or free calls over internet\n\n3. Prepaid International Calling Cards\n- Low per-minute rates\n- Can be purchased online or in stores\n- Good for occasional calls\n\n4. Mobile Apps\n- BOTIM\n- C'Me\n- Provide cheap international calling rates\n- Work over internet\n\n5. Telecom Operator International Roaming Plans\n- Specific plans for international calling\n- Can be expensive compared to other options\n\nBest recommendations:\n- WhatsApp/Internet-based calling (Free)\n- VoIP services like Skype\n- Prepaid international calling cards\n- Specific mobile carrier international packages\n\nRecommendation depends on:\n- Call frequency\n- Budget\n- Call quality desired\n- Internet availability\n\nSuggest comparing current rates and plans from different providers for the most updated options.",
